creator: Penji, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Penji is the first social learning platform for college. Students have a ton of value to offer one another, and Penji connects the dots. Use our mobile app to link up with other like-minded students for free study groups and low-cost peer tutoring.

We believe in-person interactions should remain the core of college, and thus every session coordinated by Penji is with current students from your school. Download Penji, join your campus-specific environment, and get connected to your academic peers - you'll be surprised at the difference it can make.
descriptionShort: Learn from other students for better grades, faster.

title: Penji

creator: Penji, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Penji is the central hub for tutoring, advising, and other support resources on campus. We partner with support centers at your university, allowing them to provide a modern, mobile-first, and remote-friendly experience for scheduling tutors, mentors, and coaches. Book appointments, attend drop-in hours, register for large-group sessions, meet study groups, and more, all from the app.

As recent students ourselves, we know how important friends, tutors, and mentors can be in developing your interest and confidence in different subjects. We hope Penji encourages you to take advantage of these resources more frequently.

Each university is different, so sign up to see what your university offers in Penji. Enjoy!

We partner with support centers at your university, allowing them to provide a modern, mobile-first, and remote-friendly experience for scheduling tutors, mentors, and coaches. Book appointments, attend drop-in hours, register for large-group sessions, meet study groups, and more, all from the app.

As recent students ourselves, we know how important friends, tutors, and mentors can be in developing your interest and confidence in different subjects. We hope Penji encourages you to take advantage of these resources more frequently.

Each university is different, so sign up to see what your university offers in Penji. Enjoy!

Penji is the central hub for tutoring, advising, and other support resources on campus. We partner with support centers at your university, allowing them to provide a modern, mobile-first, and remote-friendly experience for scheduling tutors, mentors, and coaches. Book appointments, attend drop-in hours, register for large-group sessions, meet study groups, and more, all from the app.

As recent students ourselves, we know how important friends, tutors, and mentors can be in developing your interest and confidence in different subjects. We hope Penji encourages you to take advantage of these resources more frequently.

Each university is different, so sign up to see what your university offers in Penji. Enjoy!
